          "text": "no tender voice like thine can peace afford."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "I need thee every hour; stay thou nearby;"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "temptations lose their power when thou art nigh."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "I need thee every hour, in joy or pain;"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "come quickly and abide, or life is vain."
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "I need thee every hour; teach me thy will;"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "and thy rich promises in me fulfill."
        }
      ],
      "number": 4
    }
  ],
  "title": "I Need Thee Every Hour"
